        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "轰！！！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "硝烟散尽后，前方的营地中只剩下一幢孤零零的建筑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "给你一分钟，把前因后果讲清楚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从我们进入这个房间开始，面前的男人就抖筛般跪倒在地，支支吾吾地一句话也说不出来。为了节约彼此的时间，我只能掏出枪，顶住了他的脑门。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "？？",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
